  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">What value of <math alttext=\"t\"><mi>t</mi>\n</math> is the solution to the equation&nbsp;<math alttext=\"0.8 t minus 0.46 equals 8 left parenthesis t minus 0.001 right parenthesis plus 1.9\"><mrow><mn>0.8</mn></mrow><mi>t</mi><mo>-</mo><mrow><mn>0.46</mn></mrow><mo>=</mo><mrow><mn>8</mn></mrow><mfenced><mrow><mi>t</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>0.001</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>+</mo><mrow><mn>1.9</mn></mrow></math>?</p>",
